      "description": "Actual Longhorn block storage consumed per namespace, ranked highest to lowest. Use this to spot which tenants/workloads dominate block storage. (Capacity is not overlaid \u2014 Grafana bar charts cannot draw a per-bar target marker; see the Capacity Planning dashboard for usage-vs-allocated projections.)"
